Titolo: Aarklash: Legacy

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Aarklash Legacy is a  tactical role-playing video game developed by Cyanide and published by Bigben Interactive. It was released in 2013 for Microsoft Windows. Inspired by the Confrontation figurines universe, the game sees the player control 4 characters from a cast of 8 to form their party.

Genere: Tactical RPG 

Valutazione: N/A
